data.description:
Beautiful Mandeville home situated on a Cul-de-sac lot. Plenty of natural light, beautiful kitchen w/ granite breakfast bar. Two large living areas, wood floors and tile. No carpet! Family room w/ fireplace and cathedral ceilings. Bonus room or possible 4th bedroom upstairs. Screened patio w/ spacious fenced yard.

Renter responsible for all utilities. Rent to own options are available!
